        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Westlake%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The U.S. Postal Service began treating Westlake as a distinct municipality on September 15 2017.",
